10	 * Design invariants:
11	 *   - All reads use db.reader() (read-only connection).
12	 *   - No SQLite writes in this module (RC-3). The attention ack endpoint
13	 *     delegates the write to an injected AckAttentionFn callback so the API
14	 *     layer itself has no write path.
15	 *   - No authentication middleware (D57).
16	 *   - No 0.0.0.0 bind path exists anywhere in this file.
